english: She was making dinner when the phone rang.
chinese: 她正在做晚饭时电话响了。

english: After lunch, Anne cleaned the table and washed dishes.
chinese: 午饭后，安妮清理了桌子并洗了碗。

english: I'll learn about cooking on the internet.
Chinese people are very good at table tennis.
chinese: 中国人非常擅长乒乓球。
这是我们最喜欢的运动。

english: He is one of the tallest basketball players in the world.
chinese: 他是世界上最高的篮球运动员之一。

english: He's going to the nearby valley to take part in a mountain bike race.
chinese: 他要去附近的山谷参加山地自行车比赛。

english: My favourite subject is science because I can do experiments during the class
chinese: 我最喜欢的科目是科学，因为我可以在课堂上做实验。

english: To make your dream come true, you should study hard
chinese: 要实现你的梦想，你应该努力学习。

english: We learned from each other in and out of class
chinese: 我们在课内外互相学习。

english: This dictionary was very cheap, and it only cost me $12.
chinese: 这本词典很便宜，我只花了12美元。
